snippet.title: ToTLS Demo - Out Now!
snippet.description:
The Tomb of The Lost Sentry demo will be publicly available on June 16th. So, here's a trailer for it.

Wishlist it on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1480910/Tomb_of_The_Lost_Sentry/

Try it on Itch!
https://spleengames.itch.io/tomb-of-the-lost-sentry

Get it from my website:
https://spleengames.com/tomb-of-the-lost-sentry/

Check out the new Devlog here!
https://spleengames.com/devlogs/ 

Join the Discord server, if you're into that kind of stuff.
discord.gg/FKbbWzuv2F
